        <h2><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Introduction to Actuarial Science</h2>
        <p>Actuarial Science is the discipline that applies mathematical and statistical methods to assess risk in insurance, finance, and other industries. Actuaries are the professionals who analyze the financial costs of risk and uncertainty, helping organizations make informed decisions about managing risk and ensuring financial stability.</p>
        
        <div class="stats-container">
            <div class="stat-box">
                <span class="stat-number">₹8-20L</span>
